store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242360/extras/a5f6f2d822d39dd57684afa6b90d222b.mp4?t=1702765479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Be aware of your surroundings</strong><br>Pay attention to what is hidden in the darkness, if you want to get out alive you will have to sharpen your wits!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242360/extras/095d2b2889ec65cc45a6dcbeab709523.poster.avif?t=1702765479\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242360/extras/095d2b2889ec65cc45a6dcbeab709523.webm?t=1702765479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242360/extras/095d2b2889ec65cc45a6dcbeab709523.mp4?t=1702765479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Your health first</strong><br>Your physical condition can worsen if you are too rash, proceed with caution.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Survival horror where you will have to explore the area where you are to be able to find the exit, be careful not to overheat your smartphone and not to strain your lungs too much.<br></li><li>3 great levels available.<br></li><li>fear and anxiety insured.</li></ul>",
